dct_title_s: City of Oxford : town map / E. G. Chandler, A.R.I.B.A., A.M.T.P.I., City Architect and Planning Officer
dct_description_sm: Map shows land use, schools mantined by local authority or direct grant, private schools, administrative boundary, boundary of local plannnig, and comprehensive development area. "Reproduced from the Ordnance Survey map with the sanction of the Controller of H.M. Stationary Office." Crown copyright reserved. Map Library does not have the companion text and the Programme map.
